The Government's Decision-

Mauje Umberkhind (Vijaybhumi), Ta. Reference No. 1 for construction of "War Memorial" of Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj at Khalapur, District Raigad. 2 By the decision of the Government here, Ma. Guardian Minister, Raigad District
A district-level committee was formed under his chairmanship. But the Collector, Raigad, referred to No. 3
Since the letter of the Committee requested to amend the said Committee, Reference No. 2 Government decisions here are overriding
The Government is approving the constitution of a revised District Level Committee as follows:
